title: Young Brisbane girl missing since this morning found safe and well - ABC News (Australian Broadcasting Corporation)
text:
Young Brisbane girl missing since this morning found safe and well Updated February 19, 2017 15:58:16 
A nine-year-old girl missing from north of Brisbane since this morning, sparking an Amber Alert from Queensland police, is found safe and well. 
The girl was reported missing in Bellmere about 9:30am. 
Queensland Police Service issued an Amber Alert about 2:30pm, and reported the girl was found soon after.
